All providers use the same core dependencies:
- `@ai-sdk/provider` (workspace dependency) - core provider interfaces (ProviderV3, ImageModelV3, etc.)
- `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` (workspace dependency) - utilities like loadApiKey, withoutTrailingSlash, etc.

For development:
- `@ai-sdk/test-server` (workspace dependency) - for testing
- `@vercel/ai-tsconfig` (workspace dependency) - shared TypeScript config
- `zod` (peer dependency) - for schema validation
- `tsup` - for building
- `vitest` - for testing

