The root `tsconfig.json` has an explicit `references` array listing each package. Adding `{ "path": "packages/pixelart" }` to it would be needed for full monorepo TypeScript project-reference builds. However, the requirement states "Do NOT modify any existing files outside packages/pixelart/". This means:

