## Complete Implementation Plan for `@ai-sdk/pixelart`

### 1. Overview

Create a new provider package at `packages/pixelart/` that implements image generation only, modeled directly after `packages/black-forest-labs/`. The package will expose a `createPixelArt` factory function returning a provider that satisfies the `ProviderV3` interface. Only the `image`/`imageModel` methods will produce a working model; `languageModel` and `embeddingModel` will throw `NoSuchModelError`.

The design is deliberately simpler than Black Forest Labs because:
- No polling is needed (synchronous API returning base64 directly).
- No file/mask/aspect-ratio conversion logic is needed.
- Provider options are limited to `style` and `pixelDensity`.

