2. `src/pixelart-image-settings.ts` -- no imports from local files
3. `src/pixelart-image-model.ts` -- imports from `pixelart-image-settings.ts`
4. `src/pixelart-provider.ts` -- imports from `pixelart-image-model.ts`, `pixelart-image-settings.ts`, `version.ts`
