- The package will still type-check independently via `pnpm type-check` inside its own directory.
- A follow-up step to add the reference to the root tsconfig would be needed only for monorepo-wide `tsc --build` from the root.

---

### 5. Architecture Decisions and Trade-offs

| Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|
